description: Have your own amazing healthy edible log grown shiitake mushrooms. We are selling Shiitake plug spawn (Wooden Dowels 100+) and 3 oz food grade wax that you can inoculate your own logs, stumps or bolts. You will grow pounds of Shiitake Mushrooms for the next few years in your own Mushroom Garden! Our Shiitake Plug Spawn features a fast spawn run, large, thick, first flush mushrooms, You will need to provide the freshly cut wood, drill and 5/16" drill bit and wax and hammer. 2funguys will answer any of your inoculation questions. If you cannot use within 1 weeks, you can place it in the refrigerator (not freezer) to keep dormant for up to 6 months before it must be used.*** 100 Shiitake Plug Spawn and 3oz wax.
